- `âœ… :test:`

### Preferred workflow

Use npm to update the version number (no tag):

- patch: `npm version patch --no-git-tag-version`
- minor: `npm version minor --no-git-tag-version`
- major: `npm version major --no-git-tag-version`

Then commit both code changes and `package.json` version bump together.